read-scan long texts in a better format

less <filename>

history | less

Useful keybindings :

q -> quit

h -> display a complete list less commands and options

/<string> -> search

n -> next match

N -> previous match

G -> move to the end of the file

1G -> move to the beginning of the file

spacebar -> page down

C^F -> page down

C^B -> page up

